---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import PageHeader from "../components/Sections/PageHeader.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Us - Church Name"
  description="Learn about our church's history, mission, values, and the people who make our community special."
>
  <PageHeader title="About Us" subtitle="Our History, Mission, and Values" />

  <!-- Statement of Faith -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
          我們相信(We Believe)
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          我們相信教會在福音真理上的共同信仰是基督裡合一的基礎。比起規模或風格更重要的是教會在教義上的堅持，這些信念驅動教會生活的各個層面。以下是
          Church on Mill
          的信仰告白。無論你是想多了解我們，還是作為會友在靈命上追求成長，我們祈求神話語中的真理能不斷鼓勵並引導你。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
        <h4>教會成員信仰告白(Church Member's Statement of Faith)</h4>
        <h3>三一真神</h3>
        <p>
          我們相信獨一的真神，永恆地存在於三位同等、合一的位格中：聖父、聖子與聖靈，彼此認識、彼此相愛並彼此榮耀。這位獨一永活的神，在祂的愛與聖潔中都是無限完全的。祂是萬物的創造者，配得一切的榮耀與敬拜；祂知道、掌管並維持萬有，並藉著祂的護理成就祂美善的旨意，為自己救贖一群子民並恢復墮落的受造界。
        </p>

        <h3>啟示</h3>
        <p>
          我們相信神以恩典向人顯明祂的存在與能力，並最終透過祂兒子——道成肉身的耶穌基督——向人啟示祂自己。神也藉著祂所默示的文字—《舊約》與《新約》共六十六卷書——啟示祂的旨意。聖經啟示關於救恩的一切，足夠引導我們信什麼、做什麼，並且在其所論及的每個領域中具有最終的權威。聖經是神完美的教導，應當被相信、順服與倚靠。
        </p>

        <h3>創造-人</h3>
        <p>
          我們相信神按照祂的形象創造了人類，為的是榮耀祂自己。亞當與夏娃在一體的婚姻中結合，這是聖經所設立性關係的唯一模式。在神的智慧中，男女雖平等但不同，彼此互補、相互成全。男女都被鼓勵服事基督，在神子民的事工中發揮他們的潛能。
        </p>

        <h3>墮落</h3>
        <p>
          我們相信亞當受造時有神的形象，卻因撒但的試探犯罪墮落，失去了原本的純潔與榮耀。罪使全地受咒詛，所有人類與神隔絕、敗壞，並且面對神公義與聖潔的忿怒，注定要承受最終與永遠的死亡。所有人類最迫切的需要就是與神和好。
        </p>

        <h3>神的救贖計畫</h3>
        <p>
          我們相信神從永恆中出於恩典，決定要從萬族萬民中拯救一大群有罪的人。神出於愛命令並懇求所有人悔改並信靠耶穌，因為在天下人間沒有賜下別的名，我們可以靠著得救。神稱義並成聖那些憑恩典信靠耶穌的人，並終將榮耀他們—這一切都是為了彰顯祂榮耀的恩典。
        </p>

        <h3>福音</h3>
        <p>
          我們相信福音就是耶穌基督的好消息，是神的大能和智慧，使相信的人得救。福音的核心是耶穌的十字架與復活。耶穌以我們的代表和中保的身分生活與受死，為我們的罪死，叫我們與神和好；祂的復活證實了祂的身份，戰勝了撒但與死亡，使我們得著永生。當人領受、相信並堅守這福音時，就從永遠的審判中被拯救，進入永恆的生命。
        </p>

        <h3>基督的救贖</h3>
        <p>
          我們相信永恆的聖子成為肉身，成為完全的神與完全的人，二性合一於一位格中。耶穌這位應許的彌賽亞，藉聖靈感孕，由童貞女馬利亞所生。祂完全順服天父，過著無罪的生活，宣講神的國度，行神蹟奇事，為滿足神的公義而被釘十字架，三日後身體復活，升天。祂是我們的大祭司、公義的中保與救主，如今坐在父神右邊，在天上與地上掌權。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Mission & Vision -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
            To know Christ and to make Him known through worship, discipleship,
            fellowship, and service.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Our Vision</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
            To be a vibrant, growing community of believers who are transformed
            by the Gospel and transforming our community with the love of
            Christ.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1493225457124-a3eb161ffa5f?w=800&h=600&fit=crop&crop=center"
            alt="Worship at our church"
            class="rounded-lg shadow-lg object-cover w-full h-full"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Values -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Our Core Values</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          These principles guide everything we do as a church community
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-8 w-8 text-primary-600"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Biblical Teaching</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We are committed to teaching God's Word faithfully and helping
            people apply it to their lives. We believe the Bible is God's
            inspired, inerrant Word and our ultimate authority.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-secondary-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-8 w-8 text-secondary-600"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Authentic Community</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We believe spiritual growth happens best in community. We foster
            genuine relationships where people can be known, loved, and
            challenged to grow in their faith.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-accent-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-8 w-8 text-accent-600"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Missional Living</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We believe every follower of Jesus is called to share His love with
            others. We equip and encourage our members to live on mission in
            their neighborhoods, workplaces, and beyond.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-green-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-8 w-8 text-green-600"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Spiritual Growth</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We are committed to helping people grow in their relationship with
            Christ, becoming more like Him in their thoughts, words, and actions
            through discipleship and spiritual practices.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-purple-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-8 w-8 text-purple-600"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M15 15l-2 5L9 9l11 4-5 2zm0 0l5 5M7.188 2.239l.777 2.897M5.136 7.965l-2.898-.777M13.95 4.05l-2.122 2.122m-5.657 5.656l-2.12 2.122"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Spirit-Led Worship</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We value authentic, heartfelt worship that glorifies God and
            transforms lives. We seek to create environments where people can
            encounter God's presence.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-yellow-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-8 w-8 text-yellow-600"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M11 4a2 2 0 114 0v1a1 1 0 001 1h3a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1a2 2 0 100 4h1a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3a1 1 0 01-1-1v-1a2 2 0 10-4 0v1a1 1 0 01-1 1H7a1 1 0 01-1-1v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a2 2 0 110-4h1a1 1 0 001-1V7a1 1 0 011-1h3a1 1 0 001-1V4z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Servant Leadership</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We believe leadership is about service, not status. We develop and
            empower leaders who model Christ-like humility and sacrifice as they
            guide others.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Church History -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Our History</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          The story of how our church has grown and evolved over the years
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="relative pl-8 sm:pl-16 py-6 group">
          <div
            class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start mb-1 group-last:before:hidden before:absolute before:left-2 sm:before:left-7 before:h-full before:px-px before:bg-gray-300 before:self-start before:-translate-x-1/2 before:translate-y-3 after:absolute after:left-2 sm:after:left-7 after:w-4 after:h-4 after:bg-primary-600 after:border-4 after:border-white after:rounded-full after:-translate-x-1/2 after:translate-y-1.5"
          >
            <time class="sm:w-28 text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase">1950</time>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Church Founded</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Our church was founded by a small group of dedicated believers
                who met in homes for Bible study and prayer.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative pl-8 sm:pl-16 py-6 group">
            <div
              class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start mb-1 group-last:before:hidden before:absolute before:left-2 sm:before:left-7 before:h-full before:px-px before:bg-gray-300 before:self-start before:-translate-x-1/2 before:translate-y-3 after:absolute after:left-2 sm:after:left-7 after:w-4 after:h-4 after:bg-primary-600 after:border-4 after:border-white after:rounded-full after:-translate-x-1/2 after:translate-y-1.5"
            >
              <time class="sm:w-28 text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase">1965</time>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">First Building</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  As the congregation grew, we purchased our first building and
                  expanded our ministries to serve the community.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative pl-8 sm:pl-16 py-6 group">
            <div
              class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start mb-1 group-last:before:hidden before:absolute before:left-2 sm:before:left-7 before:h-full before:px-px before:bg-gray-300 before:self-start before:-translate-x-1/2 before:translate-y-3 after:absolute after:left-2 sm:after:left-7 after:w-4 after:h-4 after:bg-primary-600 after:border-4 after:border-white after:rounded-full after:-translate-x-1/2 after:translate-y-1.5"
            >
              <time class="sm:w-28 text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase">1988</time>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">New Campus</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  We moved to our current location and built a larger sanctuary
                  to accommodate our growing congregation.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative pl-8 sm:pl-16 py-6 group">
            <div
              class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start mb-1 group-last:before:hidden before:absolute before:left-2 sm:before:left-7 before:h-full before:px-px before:bg-gray-300 before:self-start before:-translate-x-1/2 before:translate-y-3 after:absolute after:left-2 sm:after:left-7 after:w-4 after:h-4 after:bg-primary-600 after:border-4 after:border-white after:rounded-full after:-translate-x-1/2 after:translate-y-1.5"
            >
              <time class="sm:w-28 text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase">2010</time>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">
                  Community Center
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  We opened our community center to better serve our neighbors
                  through various outreach programs and ministries.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative pl-8 sm:pl-16 py-6 group">
            <div
              class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start mb-1 group-last:before:hidden before:absolute before:left-2 sm:before:left-7 before:h-full before:px-px before:bg-gray-300 before:self-start before:-translate-x-1/2 before:translate-y-3 after:absolute after:left-2 sm:after:left-7 after:w-4 after:h-4 after:bg-primary-600 after:border-4 after:border-white after:rounded-full after:-translate-x-1/2 after:translate-y-1.5"
            >
              <time class="sm:w-28 text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase"
                >Present</time
              >
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">
                  Continuing the Mission
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  Today, we continue to grow and adapt while staying true to our
                  mission of knowing Christ and making Him known.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
